        <ontology:hasDescription>The average per capita income (EUR/year) [Province] is 18777.43. The total Gross Value Added (GVA) (EUR million/year) [Province] is 6715.19. The primary sector share of total GVA/year [Province] is 0.13%. The secondary sector share of total GVA/year [Province] is 36.04%. The tertiary sector share of total GVA/year [Province] is 63.83%. The per capita income (EUR/year) [Region] is 18518.64. The total Gross Value Added (GVA) (EUR million/year) [Region] is 40269.69. The primary sector share of total GVA/year [Region] is 1.25%. The secondary sector share of total GVA/year [Region] is 27.14%. The tertiary sector share of total GVA/year [Region] is 71.61%.  </ontology:hasDescription>
    </NamedIndividual>
    


